# 9. Constraint Engine

Evita salidas incoherentes.

```json
{
  "constraints": {
    "hardConstraints": [
      "The generated variation must preserve the core genre identity unless the user explicitly changes genre.",
      "The output must not reproduce copyrighted text.",
      "Character actions must remain consistent with adjusted motivations."
    ],
    "softConstraints": [
      "Maintain emotional coherence with the new variable set.",
      "Preserve cause-and-effect clarity.",
      "Avoid abrupt ending shifts without narrative bridge."
    ],
    "identityConstraints": {
      "preserveCoreConflict": true,
      "preserveThemeContinuity": true,
      "allowToneShift": true
    }
  }
}
```

Tipos:

* `hardConstraints`: nunca romper
* `softConstraints`: deseables
* `identityConstraints`: preservan ADN de la obra

